Summary: Hi Saaem, Grand to hear from you—and it sounds as though you’re enjoying time in the City. Regarding the knowledge test, please consider just going to a DMV and enter the non-appointment queue. The quietest days are typically Wednesdays—but I would suggest going early. Be sure to complete the online application and make sure you have all the required documents. Let me know when you’ve completed the 1st step and are scheduling the driving test so I can accompany you to the DMV for the driving test. Best, --Emi Tuvey, Destination Services Consultant.
